## Limitations

This report is based on available online sources and may not encompass all perspectives on the topic. The search was limited to English-language sources, which may exclude relevant international viewpoints. Additionally, the report focuses on the benefits of free college and does not extensively cover potential drawbacks or counterarguments. Further research could provide a more balanced view by including these aspects.

